snippet.title: David R. B.
snippet.description:
Hey everyone, David here! 

I'm currently solo developing my first indie game: Arcadian Rift, a sci fi FPS being made with the Unreal Engine. I am also the founder of Black Plasma Studios where I created the Minecraft animated series: Songs of War. 

I love music, good stories, and PIZZA!
